data.description: NEW YEAR, NEW HOME!  This is the home that you have been searching for.  Better than new! Move-in ready! Absolutely beautiful single family home shows pride of ownership. When you walk up to this home you will be greeted by the Cozy front porch. Step inside and you will fall in love with the bright open 2 story entryway with a cascading staircase. Travel into the Gorgeous kitchen and you will find New appliances, island with seating, granite countertops, custom backsplash. Love the view of the backyard from the kitchen window. The sliding glass doors from the kitchen lead to the huge backyard. The Open floorplan makes this home just flow from one room to another. Spacious Family room. Separate Dining room provides options for additional space. First floor Home Office space with plenty of natural light.  Convenient First floor laundry room.  Upstairs you will find 4 large bedrooms. The owners Suite features walk-in closet, full bath with double bowl vanity, walk-in shower and soaking tub. Downstairs you will find a large open unfinished basement. The basement has a  full size window so you could easily add an additional bedroom. So much room to add more living space and the basement is equipped with a bathroom rough-in to add an additional bathroom. The driveway was just sealed after the pictures were taken, so come check out the freshly sealed driveway! Plenty of parking in the Oversized 2 car garage. One of the largest lots in the neighborhood. So many possibilities for this amazing outdoor space. Rare find-Level backyard incredible .62 acres. Great location. Minutes to Codorus State Park. Close to the MD line for Easy commute. Schedule your showings now! What are you waiting for! This Gorgeous Home is Ready for you! Ask about Financing options! Help towards closing costs$$! Low interest rate options!
